text: Isabella Wieser is a road cyclist from Austria. She represented her nation at the 2002, 2005 and 2006 UCI Road World Championships. She won the Austrian National Road Race Championships in 2002. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:Austrian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
